# How to Play

Colossal Cave Adventure is a text adventure game. You explore a vast cave system, collecting treasures and solving puzzles.

## Navigation

Click the direction links (North, South, East, West, Up, Down, In, Out) to move between rooms.

## Commands

Use "Enter a command" to type freeform commands:

* TAKE / GET — pick up an object (e.g., TAKE LAMP)
* DROP — put down an object
* OPEN / UNLOCK — open something (e.g., OPEN GRATE)
* CLOSE / LOCK — close something
* ON / OFF — turn the lamp on or off
* LOOK — examine your surroundings in detail
* INVENTORY — see what you're carrying
* SCORE — check your score
* EAT / DRINK — consume items
* WAVE — wave an object
* THROW — throw an object
* XYZZY — a magic word...
* HELP — get hints

## Tips

* Take the lamp from the building — you'll need it in the cave.
* Get the keys to unlock the grate.
* Explore carefully; the cave is vast and full of surprises.
* Deposit treasures in the building for points.

